const iState = {
  name: [],
  opacityname: [],
  parentname: [],
  parentnamewater: [],
  drawerdata: '',
  leftdrawerdata: false,
  rightdrawerdata: 'true',
  basemapname: 'openstreetmap',
  geometryType: 'None',
  strokecolor: '#0A0A48',
  fillcolor: '#0000ff',
  strokewidth: '1',
  vectoredittoggle: false,
  firstname: 'Arman',
}
const reducer = (state = iState, action) => {
  if (action.type == 'CHANGE_NAME')
    return {
      ...state,
      name: action.payload,
    }

  return state
}
export default reducer
